        <font size='4'><b>MOVIE THEATER EXPANDS THANKS TO DANIEL RAINEY</b></font><br>
                                <img src='http://graphics.millsberry.com/site_gfx/interiors/gazette/gazette_20080710.jpg' border='1' width='280' height='200'>
                        </div>
        <div id='gazette_byline'><em>By Everett F. Stevens<br>Staff Writer</em></div>
        <b>Thursday, July 10, 2008</b> &mdash;
    Our beloved <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/theater.phtml">Millsberry Movie Theater</a> has received an upgrade thanks to Daniel Rainey, Millsberry native and director of the critically acclaimed film &quot;Midnight Sunshine.&quot; <br><br>At the opening of the theater, Rainey was on hand as he signed autographs and fielded questions from the press.<br><br>&quot;I&#039;m so happy to have been able to give the people of Millsberry this addition to their movie theater.&quot;<br><br>&quot;I believe film is a really important part of everyone&#039;s life. And of course, for something that&#039;s really important, like movies, we need to give this pastime the appropriate venue.&quot;<br><br>&quot;I hope that everyone loves this new theater expansion as much as I do. We&#039;ll be able to show many more movies than we were able to before,&quot; added Rainey.<br><br>
<br>
Several high profile Millsberry citizens were in attendance at the theater opening.<br><br>&quot;This new theater expansion will bring so much to Millsberry,&quot; commented Mayor Trumble during the opening ceremony.<br><br>&quot;As I&#039;m sure everyone else is, I&#039;m looking forward to having more movies to see on Friday nights.&quot;<br><br>&quot;Daniel Rainey is so generous for donating this theater expansion. On behalf of Millsberry, I would like to thank him for such an outstanding contribution to the community,&quot; added Trumble.  <br><br>Loretta Rivers, owner of Studio T and Wearhouse, was also on hand for the opening.<br><br>&quot;It&#039;s so great to see new additions like this to the city. It&#039;s one of the many reasons I love living here so much&quot;, said Rivers.<br><br>&quot;The chairs were extra comfy too, which was a plus. I really love the overall design of everything. Daniel&#039;s got a really great eye for detail,&quot; added Rivers.<br><br>The new theater will be screening shows regularly, so there will be plenty of opportunities to catch some movie magic. <br><br>Just sit back, relax, and <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/theater.phtml">enjoy the show.</a>
    </div>

